{
  "text": "In order to assess reorganization in the vascular wall, several types of in vitro models have been applied, e.g vascular smooth muscle cells (VSMC) cultures [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] , co-cultures of endothelial cells and VSMC [CITATION_3] , fibroblast-like cells in 3-dimensional gel structure [CITATION_4] or explant-derived VSMC [CITATION_5] [CITATION_6] .",
